OL,4,Ccalls for wide reforms and smaller
OL,5,Cforces
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,8,FMark Rowley has called for sweeping
OL,9,Freforms of the policing system, which
OL,10,Fhe says needs to change "quite
OL,11,Fdramatically".
OL,13,FSpeaking on Sky News' Sunday Morning
OL,14,Fwith Trevor Phillips, Rowley said
OL,15,Fpolicing reforms were overdue and
OL,16,Fdescribed the current model as "out of
OL,17,Fdate for the challenges of today".
