OL,7,FThe commissioner called for a
OL,8,Freduction in the 43 police forces in
OL,9,FEngland and Wales, saying it would
OL,10,Fpave the way for greater investment in
OL,11,Ftechnology.
OL,13,F"We are overdue big police reforms,"
OL,14,Fhe said. "The current policing model
OL,15,Fis a tweaked and bastardised version
OL,16,Fof what was designed in a 1962 royal
OL,17,Fcommission.
