OL,3,CPolice Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley
OL,4,Ccalls for wide reforms and smaller
OL,5,Cforces
OL,7,F"It is so out of date for the
OL,8,Fchallenges today. A unique thing about
OL,9,Fwhere we are today, police leaders
OL,10,Facross the system were all of a common
OL,11,Fmindset that the system needs to
OL,12,Fchange quite dramatically.
OL,14,F"So you might say we're prepared to be
OL,15,Fthe turkeys who vote for Christmas in
OL,16,Fterms of fewer police forces.
OL,18,F"People will immediately say 'this is
OL,19,Fgoing to damage local policing' `
OL,20,Fquite the opposite.
