OL,12,FSir Mark's calls for reform come a
OL,13,Fweek after figures showed that the
OL,14,Fnumber of homicides recorded in London
OL,15,Fhas dropped to its lowest level in
OL,16,Fmore than a decade.
OL,18,FThere were 97 homicides in 2025, down
OL,19,F11% from 109 in 2024, according to
OL,20,Fdata from the Met.
