OL,4,Ccalls for wide reforms and smaller
OL,5,Cforces
OL,7,FThat represented the lowest number
OL,8,Frecorded since 95 homicides 11 years
OL,9,Fago, in 2014.
OL,11,FAccording to the Met, despite London's
OL,12,Fgrowing population in the last decade,
OL,13,Flast year had the lowest homicide rate
OL,14,Fper capita on record, 1.1 per 100,000,
OL,15,Flower than other major cities
OL,16,Fworldwide, such as New York at 2.8,
OL,17,FBerlin at 3.2 and Paris at 1.6 per
OL,18,F100,000.
