OL,3,CPolice Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley
OL,4,Ccalls for wide reforms and smaller
OL,5,Cforces
OL,7,F"The point about a homicide rate per
OL,8,Fcapita in London is lower than it's
OL,9,Fever been," Sir Mark added. "That's an
OL,10,Fextraordinary fact.
OL,12,F"These are quite remarkable
OL,13,Fstatistics. And of course, it's not
OL,14,Fjust about policing ` there's health
OL,15,Fservices, there's all the diversion
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,F"But we're taking more weapons off the
OL,19,Fstreets. We're putting more organised
OL,20,Fcriminals in prison."
